title: 'Boys and Girl - Week 3 Seahawks Preview, Slowing Down Russell Wilson, Injuries
itunes:title: 'Boys and Girl - Week 3 Seahawks Preview, Slowing Down Russell Wilson, Injuries
description:
On today’s episode of the 'Boys and Girl Podcast, Jane is off, but Bobby is joined by RJ Ochoa and Kelsey Charles from SB Nation’s Blogging the Boys. The trio discuss Dallas’ tough injury situation, the Cowboys’ lack of pass rush, and how to slow down Russell Wilson. Plus, comedian and Seahawks fan Dustin Nickerson stops by to chat about the game. Follow Jane and Bobby on Twitter and subscribe to get all the latest inside information from two of the most connected people in the Cowboys’ community.
